message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper is about visual question answering (VQA) and the use of external knowledge resources to answer questions. This falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning models (cs.AI, cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques to tackle the task.
